  <div class="container" role="main" id="main">
    <header>
      <h1>My Enhanced Simple Page</h1>
      <p>Clean starter template with improved styling, accessibility, and user experience.</p>
      <nav aria-label="Main navigation">
        <a href="#about">About</a>
        <a href="#features">Features</a>
        <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
      </nav>
    </header>

    <section id="about" class="hero" aria-labelledby="about-heading">
      <h2 id="about-heading">Welcome</h2>
      <p>This section introduces the page. Using semantic HTML tags like <code>&lt;section&gt;</code>, <code>&lt;article&gt;</code>, and <code>&lt;nav&gt;</code> improves both accessibility and SEO.</p>
      <p>I've enhanced the original design with better spacing, subtle animations, and improved form styling while maintaining the clean aesthetic.</p>
      <button onclick="showWelcome()">Click me</button>
    </section>

    <section id="features" aria-labelledby="features-heading">
      <h2 id="features-heading">Features</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Fully responsive design with mobile-friendly breakpoints</li>
        <li>Semantic HTML structure (header, nav, main, footer)</li>
        <li>Enhanced accessibility features including skip link</li>
        <li>Improved form styling with focus states</li>
        <li>Subtle animations and transition effects</li>
        <li>Better color scheme with consistent variables</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section id="contact" aria-labelledby="contact-heading">
      <h2 id="contact-heading">Contact</h2>
      <form id="contact-form" aria-label="Contact form">
        <label>
          Name
          <input type="text" name="name" required placeholder="Your name" />
        </label>
        
        <label>
          Email
          <input type="email" name="email" required placeholder="Your email address" />
        </label>
        
        <label>
          Message
          <textarea name="message" rows="4" required placeholder="How can we help you?"></textarea>
        </label>
        
        <button type="submit">Send Message</button>
      </form>
    </section>

    <footer>
      <p>Made with ❤️ — <small>© <span id="year"></span> All rights reserved</small></p>
    </footer>
